snippet.title: Jawan: Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya Extended Version (Hindi): Shah Rukh Khan |Atlee |Anirudh |Nayanthara
snippet.description:
Join the ultimate dance party with this blockbuster father-son duo as they bring the magic of #NotRamaiyaVastavaiya to life. Full song out now!

Jawan is a high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in society. 

Watch #Jawan in cinemas - in Hindi, Tamil & Telugu.

Book tickets now - https://linktr.ee/Jawan_BookTicketsNow

♪Full Song Available on♪ 
JioSaavn: https://bit.ly/3srnLI5
Spotify: https://bit.ly/3ssmbG1
Hungama: https://bit.ly/3OW4upT
Apple Music: https://bit.ly/3OYPyau
Amazon Prime Music: https://bit.ly/44vEozG
Wynk: https://bit.ly/3L0roLy
Resso: https://bit.ly/47UA7Zy
YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/3OWNbov

Music Credits:
Language - Hindi
Song Title - Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya 
Album / Movie - Jawan
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Kumaar
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander, Vishal Dadlani & Shilpa Rao
Choreographer - Vaibhavi Merchant 

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Whistle - Satish Raghunathan
Tabla - MT Aditya
Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay
Additional Keyboard Programmed by Arish-Pradeep PJ

Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya
Music Editor - Harish Ram L H
Recorded at Albuquerque Records, Chennai. Engineered by Srinivasan M, Shivakiran S, Rajesh Kannan, Jishnu Vijayan
YRF Studios, Mumbai, Engineered by Vijay Dayal & Chinmay
Mixed by Vinay Sridhar & Srinivasan M at Albuquerque Records, Chennai
Mastered by Luca Pretolesi at Studio DMI, Las Vegas Assisted by Alistair Pintus 
Music Coordinator - Velavan B

Lyrics:

Dance with me now I can’t break away
Aaj sari fikreiin tu shake away
Shake away
Dil thirakta dance wale groove pe
Nachun mai to step mera vekh ve

Vekh ve
Aaj sare kaam kal pe talke
Tak dhina dhin nache jayein taal pe
Disko jaz blues sare bhoolke
Desi wale geet pe tu jhoolke
Pehle kiya chaiya chaiya re
Ab kar tha tha thaiyya
Ramiya vasta vaiya..!
Antra

Sama mazedar hua houle houle
Thoda nashedar hua
Man ye dole
Aaj koi nachta hua sa jadu
Sar pe swar hua
Dil ye bole
Doobi khushiyon mein
Raat apni jabse suraj dhala
Chodh sharmana aaj nachle pair chakkle zara

Pahle kiya chaiya chaiiya re
Ab kar tata thaiya
Ramiya vasta vaiyaa..!


___________________________________

Nain tumko  chuney,,
bs baat dil ki suney ,,
Dunia ko bhool kar ,,
Tere hi khaab buney ,,
Tujhme or khuda me koi fark na jaane ,,
Humto deewane deewane deewane ,,
Tere deewane deewane deewane ,

Tujhme or khuda me koi fark na jaane ,,

Hum to deewane deewane ….

Tujhey apna hai kehna ve , 
Mai tere nal rehna ve,,
dekhne k dhundhay bahanay ,,

Humto deewanay ,,deewane ,,

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

This channel is providing primarily regional news of Madhya Pradesh & Chhattisgarh besides national, International, sports and other main news of public interests. Our wide network of reporters in rural and urban areas has made us one of the most reliable news channels of Madhya Pradesh and Chhattisgarh.

snippet.title: Two types of husband | Awareness | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
Antenatal care (ANC) plays a pivotal role in ensuring a healthy pregnancy and safe childbirth. Regular ANC check-ups help monitor the health of both the mother and the developing fetus, enabling early detection and management of potential complications. When it comes to childbirth, opting for institutional delivery in a healthcare facility under skilled birth attendants significantly reduces maternal and neonatal mortality rates. These controlled environments provide necessary medical interventions and emergency care if required during labor and delivery. Moreover, after birth, timely and comprehensive child vaccinations are crucial to protect infants from various preventable diseases, building their immune system and ensuring a healthy start to life. Vaccinations safeguard children's health and contribute to the overall well-being of the community by preventing the spread of contagious illnesses.
This video is produced by
Peren District Administration under Beti Bacho Beti Padhao (BBBP) on Girl child/Women health related issues.

snippet.title: Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom | Trailer
snippet.description:
One king will lead us all. #Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom - Only in theaters December 20.

Director James Wan and Aquaman himself, Jason Momoa—along with Patrick Wilson, Amber Heard, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II and Nicole Kidman—return in the sequel to the highest-grossing DC film of all time: “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom.”

Having failed to defeat Aquaman the first time, Black Manta, still driven by the need to avenge his father’s death, will stop at nothing to take Aquaman down once and for all. This time Black Manta is more formidable than ever before, wielding the power of the mythic Black Trident, which unleashes an ancient and malevolent force. To defeat him, Aquaman will turn to his imprisoned brother Orm, the former King of Atlantis, to forge an unlikely alliance. Together, they must set aside their differences in order to protect their kingdom and save Aquaman’s family, and the world, from irreversible destruction.

All returning to the roles they originated, Jason Momoa plays Arthur Curry/Aquaman, now balancing his duties as both the King of Atlantis and a new father; Patrick Wilson is Orm, Aquaman’s half-brother and his nemesis, who must now step into a new role as his brother’s reluctant ally; Amber Heard is Mera, Atlantis’ Queen and mother of the heir to the throne; Yahya Abdul-Mateen II is Black Manta, committed more than ever to avenge his father’s death by destroying Aquaman, his family and Atlantis; and Nicole Kidman as Atlanna, a fierce leader and mother with the heart of a warrior. Also reprising their roles are Dolph Lundgren as King Nereus and Randall Park as Dr. Stephen Shin.

Directed by Wan, “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom” is produced by Peter Safran, Wan and Rob Cowan. The executive producers are Galen Vaisman and Walter Hamada.

The screenplay is by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, from a story by James Wan & David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick and Jason Momoa & Thomas Pa’a Sibbett, based on characters from DC, Aquaman created by Paul Norris and Mort Weisinger. 

Joining Wan behind-the-camera is his sterling team of “Aquaman” artisans: director of photography Don Burgess (“The Conjuring 2”), production designer Bill Brzeski (“Jumanji: The Next Level”), editor Kirk Morri (“Furious 7”), composer Rupert Gregson-Williams (“Wonder Woman”) and music supervisor is Michelle Silverman (“Malignant”). Visual effects supervisor Nick Davis (“The Clash of the Titans” films, “The Dark Knight”) and costume designer Richard Sale (“Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness,” “Ready Player One”) also join.

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents An Atomic Monster / A Peter Safran Production of A James Wan Film, “Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom,” set to open in theaters internationally beginning 20 December 2023 and in North America on December 20, 2023; it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.description:
#kirtimehra is a well-known #youtuber . She has talked openly about all aspects of her #life. How she created a #youtubechannel and what was her journey to get here She also became emotional, remembering many incidents in her life. There came a time in her life when she lived on salt and bread. Kirti Mehra's father had a dream that his daughter would someday be on TV. Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं.

snippet.title: 'തെരുവിൽ ഇംഗ്ലീഷ് സംസാരിക്കുന്ന യാചക, റീൽ വൈറലായതും പഴയ അധ്യാപികയെ തേടി വിദ്യാർത്ഥി എത്തി'
snippet.description:
This is a video posted on the Instagram account of a content creator named Muhammad Ashiq on September 9. This old woman named Marilyn became a teacher. They were natives of Myanmar and came here after marrying an Indian. Within 2 days of seeing this reel uploaded by Mohammad Ashiq, one of Marilyn's favorite students who took away her tuition was coming to the streets looking for her #love #teacher #happiness #life #peace #world 




മുഹമ്മദ് ആഷിക് എന്ന കണ്ടെന്റ് ക്രിയേറ്ററുടെ ഇൻസ്റ്റാഗ്രാം അക്കൗണ്ടിൽ സെപ്റ്റംബർ 9 നു വന്ന വീഡിയോ ആണിത്. മെർലിൻ എന്ന ഈ വൃദ്ധ ഒരു അധ്യാപികയായിന്നു. മ്യാൻമർ സ്വദേശിയായിരുന്ന ഇവർ ഇന്ത്യക്കാരനെ വിവാഹം ചെയ്താണ് ഇവിടെ എത്തുന്നത്. മുഹമ്മദ് ആഷിക് അപ്ലോഡ് ചെയ്ത ഈ റീല് കണ്ട് 2 ദിവസത്തിനുള്ളിൽ തന്നെ മെർലിൻ പണ്ട് ട്യൂഷൻ എടുത്തുകൊടുത്ത അവരുടെ പ്രിയപ്പെട്ട ഒരു വിദ്യാർത്ഥി അവരെ തേടി തെരുവിൽ എത്തുകയായിരുന്നു.

snippet.description:

Episode 3878: Paryushan Ki Shuruaat
--------------------------------------------------------
When Tapu Sena arrives at the Gada home, he informs him that he will be unable to join the group since he needs to transport Champaklal to Palitana. Tapu Sena becomes enthralled after hearing about fasting and its purpose. Champaklal tells the Tapu Sena the narrative, and they are encouraged to participate. Jetha comes to the Gada store and is overjoyed since his store is packed with people. Later, a customer is irritated when Bagha makes a payment error. Jetha becomes concerned when he witnesses this. Stay tuned for additional info!
 
Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3878, 16 Sep 2023

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 339
snippet.description:
'ഉപ്പും മുളകും' വീട്ടിൽ മോഷണഭീഷണിയിലോ? കള്ളനെ പിടിക്കാനൊരുങ്ങി നീലു. ഒപ്പം കേശുവും. പിന്തിരിപ്പിക്കാനുള്ള ലെച്ചുവിന്റെ ശ്രമം വിഫലം. വരാനിരിക്കുന്ന പൊല്ലാപ്പുകൾ കാത്തിരുന്ന് തന്നെ കാണാം!!

Is the 'Uppum Mulakum' household under the threat of theft? Neelu is on the verge of apprehending the thief, with Keshu providing full support. Lechu's attempt to resist has failed. Let's wait and see what happens in ''Uppum Mulakum''!

localized.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 339
localized.description:
'ഉപ്പും മുളകും' വീട്ടിൽ മോഷണഭീഷണിയിലോ? കള്ളനെ പിടിക്കാനൊരുങ്ങി നീലു. ഒപ്പം കേശുവും. പിന്തിരിപ്പിക്കാനുള്ള ലെച്ചുവിന്റെ ശ്രമം വിഫലം. വരാനിരിക്കുന്ന പൊല്ലാപ്പുകൾ കാത്തിരുന്ന് തന്നെ കാണാം!!

Is the 'Uppum Mulakum' household under the threat of theft? Neelu is on the verge of apprehending the thief, with Keshu providing full support. Lechu's attempt to resist has failed. Let's wait and see what happens in ''Uppum Mulakum''!

snippet.title: DESH KA DHONI | OFFICIAL TRAILER | Flying Beast
snippet.description:
It's the story of a middle-class, hard-working man, whose journey began in Kanpur.  Like any other middle-class guy, he chooses to attend IIT under parental pressure rather than chasing his passion to become a cricketer. Lingering within him is the remorse of never affording his passion the opportunity it deserved.

He idolized Mr. MS Dhoni, who didn't give up and was persistent in achieving his dreams and passion of becoming a cricketer, irrespective of every possible hurdle in life.
His decision to portray his love for his idol through his hard work, which is unparalleled.

Gaurav then, gets on a maiden mammoth journey of a 2400km bicycle ride from Delhi to Chennai in the extreme weather and heat conditions of the month of May to pay a legendary tribute to MS Dhoni by collecting wishes for him, all across the country.


Gaurav's Instagram https://www.instagram.com/taneja.gaurav/
Ritu's Instagram https://www.instagram.com/riturathee/

I graduated from IIT Kharagpur and currently work as a captain with a domestic carrier.

snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 15 Pro | Apple
snippet.description:
The new iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max are ready for action. Built with aerospace-grade titanium for our lightest, most powerful Pro models ever.

The new Pro camera system pushes the limits of what’s possible on a smartphone, giving photographers the equivalent of seven pro lenses ranging from 13 mm on the Ultra Wide camera to 120 mm on the 5x Telephoto camera on iPhone 15 Pro Max.

Filmmakers can now record video in ProRes 4K at 60 fps directly to an external drive. The addition of a USB-C connector brings superfast USB 3 transfer speeds, along with support for pro formats that massively improve the workflow between shooting and post-production.

The new design also includes a customizable Action button for quicker access to your favorite feature.*

And the A17 Pro chip with a 6-core GPU introduces a whole new level of immersive mobile gaming performance. 

In short, the new titanium iPhone 15 Pro is our most powerful photo-taking, movie-making, game-playing iPhone ever.

Learn more about iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max: https://apple.co/3PBuiJq

Audio Descriptions: https://apple.co/44QCI3W

#AppleEvent #iPhone15Pro #iPhone

*Translate action is coming in an update later this year

Episode 3877: B.K. Su
--------------------------------------------------------
Purush Mandali of Gokuldham converses about business at Taarak's house. Jetha reaches home and is shocked to find the door open. He enters the house and finds Bapuji sleeping on the couch, he tries to pick him up in his hands and shift him into his bedroom but he wakes up and gets frightened.  Jetha asks Bhide to publish his book of thoughts but later disagrees with Bhide's 'suvichaar' on the society board as he finds it wrong What happens next? Watch the episode to learn more!!

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Lyrics -
लड़की :- बानी तोहसे नाराज रंगबाज राजाजी
 हम त रोव तानी काट के पियाज राजाजी

लड़का :- जुग जुग जिय ए करेजा काहे कह तारु आग लागल हो 
ए धनी हो जहिया से जिनिगी मे अइलू तहिये से हमार भाग जागल हो
कोरस :- ए भउजी हो जहिया से घरवा मे अइलू भइया के हमार भाग जागल हो

लड़का :- एगो साड़ी के पाछा देबेलु गारी 
नाही करेलु बतिया तू प्यारी प्यारी

लड़की :- अब त तोहरा से हम नाही बोलब ए राजा

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 338
snippet.description:
നീലുവിനെ പറ്റിച്ച് പാറമട വീട്ടിലെ കുട്ടിപ്പട. പക്ഷെ, ഒളിച്ചുവയ്ക്കാനുള്ള ശ്രമങ്ങളൊക്കെ പാളുകയും ചെയ്തു. പാറുക്കുട്ടിയിൽ നിന്നും കുട്ടിപ്പടയുടെ രഹസ്യമറിയാൻ ശ്രമിക്കുകയാണ് നീലു..
'Uppum Mulakum' is the favorite sitcom of Malayalees. The show, which travels through Balu, Neelu and their four children's lives. This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?

Bharti TV के LOL Podcast के पहले एपिसोड में, भारती और हर्ष ने जया किशोरी जी को अपने गेस्ट के तौर पर आमंत्रित किया। उन्होंने चर्चा की कि बच्चों के जीवन में आध्यात्मिकता कैसे पेश किया जा सकता है। उन्होंने माता-पिता के लिए मूलभूत सुझाव और अपने व्यक्तिगत अनुभवों का सांझा किया। इसका उद्देश्य बच्चों के पालन-पोषण में आध्यात्मिक मूल्यों और प्रैक्टिकल सुझावों की समझ प्रदान करना है। यह एपिसोड वे लोगों के लिए बेहद महत्वपूर्ण है जो अपने बच्चों को आध्यात्मिक दृष्टिकोण से पालना चाहते हैं। भारती, हर्ष , और जया किशोरी के साथ जुड़ें और उनके साथ जुड़कर देखें कि आने वाली पीढ़ियों के पालने में आध्यात्मिकता का महत्व क्या है।

In the debut of LOL Podcast on Bharti TV, Bharti and Haarsh invite Jaya Kishori to discuss introducing spirituality to kids. They share insights and tips for parents and caregivers. Perfect for anyone interested in raising spiritually aware children. 

(00:00) - Start of the episode   
(02:02) - Bachchon ke jeevan me spirituality  ko kaise introduce karein ?
(06:17) - Bhagwan ka bachpan 
(09:01) - Bharti ki shararate 
(10:14) - Female spiritual leaders itni kam Kyu hai...?
(14:36) - Shaadi
(22:55) - Jaya Kishori & food 
(28:23) - Boogie Woogie
(30:13) - kisi ladke ne kabhi propose kiya hai ?
(33:54) - pariwaar ko ek saath khaana, khana chahiye 
(34:47) - spirituality & success.
(43:05) - Shrimad Bhagavad story .
(45:01) - Meaning of bhagwat Puran 
(50:50) - How to be relatable among youth?
(54:07) - Jaya Kishori listens to Rajeshwaranand Ji Maharaj
(59:01) - End Note 

#jayakishori #podcast #bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya

WATCH CLIPS HERE : https://youtube.com/@BhartiTV-LOLPodcast?si=IAYnTkA8elQ3ipus

snippet.title: BPraak - Zohrajabeen (Teaser) | Randeep Hooda | Priyanka Chahar Choudhary | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies proudly presents the official music video of 'Zohrajabeen' title track from BPraak’s debut album. The soulful voice and composition of BPraak, paired with Jaani's touching lyrics, come alive in a visual masterpiece directed by Arvindr Khaira, featuring Bollywood icon Randeep Hooda alongside the captivating Priyanka Chahar Choudhary. Arranged and programmed by the talented Gaurav Dev and Kartik Dev, this heart-wrenching story is set to linger. 

Stay tuned, full music video drops on 15th September. Mark your calendars and don’t forget to subscribe to the Desi Melodies YouTube channel. 

#RandeepHooda #BPraak #Jaani #PriyankaChaharChoudhary

A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. Yella seruma
Jothege yella seruma

Josh ali tamte yetige

Ganesha

Ganesha

नमस्ते दोस्तों!
The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 196th Episode में आप सभी का स्वागत है. आज के Podcast में हमारे साथ जुड़ चुके हैं मशहूर कवि Kumar Vishwas, जिनकी कविताओं को लोगों से ढ़ेर सारा प्यार मिलता है। साथ ही ये हिंदी के Professor भी रह चुके हैं। अपने जीवन के कुछ साल इन्होंने राजनीति में भी बिताए हैं। 

इस Podcast में हम बात करेंगे ढ़ेर सारी बातें Kumar Vishwas की Life Story, Political Journey, Political Ideology, Anna Hazare, PM Modi, 2024 Elections और Social Media के बारे में।

साथ-ही-साथ हम बात करेंगे शिव तांडव का रहस्य, Spirituality और Religion, Politicians, GenZ की Problems और Creative Transformation के बारे में और भी ढ़ेर सारी बातें। 

मैं आशा करता हूँ कि ये Video आप सभी Viewers को पसंद आएगा। खास तौर पर उन सभी को जिन्हें Kumar Vishwas की Life के बारे में जानने में Interest है। 

Future Of India, Who Will Be India's Next PM और Young Leaders In Politics जैसी चीज़ों के बारे में हम Discuss करेंगे इस Hindi Podcast में सिर्फ और सिर्फ आपके Favourite BeerBiceps Hindi Channel Ranveer Allahbadia पर।
